        </p>
        <ul
          style={{
            listStyle: "none",
            padding: 0,
            marginTop: "0.5rem",
            fontFamily: "ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace",
            fontSize: "0.82rem",
          }}
        >
          <li>slope = {fmt(manifest.calibrationSlope.slope)}</li>
          <li>
